name: Ziggurat - Shinoda Tribute
description:
Visual/Audio Tribute to Mike Shinoda and Ziggurats.
Lyrics: Apparently, I do wanna be like Mike.
He came into our scene, broke it with one strike.
Melody and PFP we all had to buy.
Some drama on the drop but secondary flies.
Twice the art of any other PFP.
But some don’t value music they still asleep.
That's an opportunity to buy cheap .
Don’t underestimate this NFT!
